# This repo hosts TWO Vercel projects that share the same root:
#   • the Vite app (src/)        → closeeye.in
#   • closeeye-next/ (Next.js)   → closeeye-next.vercel.app
#
# BOTH projects read THIS root .vercelignore during upload, so we must NOT
# exclude all of closeeye-next/ — doing so starved the closeeye-next project's
# own build of its source ("No Next.js version detected"). Exclude only the
# heavy folders that NEITHER web build needs (native shells, build output).
closeeye-next/android
closeeye-next/ios
closeeye-next/.next
